{"tid":1936104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拜仁球星哥列斯卡和甘美治捐贈100萬  創立捐款平台對抗武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-21T04:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T16:07:23.000Z","uid":34471,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab87372d7cb3ed9d2bfe4b472c1ddd2097be71d","tid":1936104,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"蘋果<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎在全球不斷擴散，不少體壇名人都利用自己聲望，打算為抗疫出一分力。其中德甲班霸拜仁慕尼黑兩名大將，中場哥列斯卡及甘美治周五宣佈，合共捐款100萬歐元，並創立一個名叫「We Kick Corona」的平台，希望世人繼續捐款，以幫助正與武漢肺炎對抗的社會組織、慈善機構和衞生機構。據報德國國家隊的隊友，更已向他們的抗疫平台捐款250萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\nGoretzka<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nKimchi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d360499cdaad39c79bca7aae9366f057021db55f","tid":1936104,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db9cc42653b020457ca0be61829775eee39fe86","tid":1936104,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c6abe93b9db499ac16e6f086ec3877f886f79e","tid":1936104,"uid":141681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"利雲好似都捐左一百萬歐"}]}